nm:output.nm:control_stream:
$PROB RUN# 101
$INPUT C ID TIME EVID AMT CMT SS II ADDL RATE LAGT MODE DUR2 RAT2 BIOAV DV
$DATA ../../data/1001.csv IGNORE=C
$SUBROUTINES ADVAN2 TRANS2
$PK
TVCL=THETA(1) CL=TVCL*EXP(ETA(1))
TVV2=THETA(2) V=TVV2*EXP(ETA(2))
TVKA=THETA(3) KA=TVKA*EXP(ETA(3))
ALAG2 = LAGT F2 = BIOAV
IF(MODE.EQ.1) R2 = RAT2 IF(MODE.EQ.2) D2 = DUR2
$ERROR IPRED=A(2)/(V/1000) Y=IPRED*EXP(ERR(1))
CP = IPRED
$THETA (1.1, FIX) ;; CL (20, FIX) ;; V (1.5, FIX) ;; KA
$OMEGA 0.0 FIX 0.0 FIX 0.0 FIX
$SIGMA 0.00 FIX
$TABLE FILE=TAB TIME EVID CP IPRED PRED DV NOPRINT ONEHEADER NOAPPEND
$SIMULATION (2674474) ONLYSIMULATION
